familyowned business that sells chainsaw supplies to retailers he 
has served on the vilas county board of supervisors since 1983 and 
was elected to the northland pines school district in eagle river 
in 1981 
the recall was organized by a group called stop treaty 
abusewisconsin which claims that indian treaties are unfair 
because they give indians unequal rights 
no state representative has ever been successfuly recalled in 
wisconsin the last recall election was in 1932 when republican 
sen otto mueller of wausau retained his seat 
