require senate confirmation 
when speculation surfaced that jonathan fiechter senior deputy 
in charge of policy at the agency might be named as interim 
director sampl industry officials raised questions over the legality 
of any actions taken by an acting director who was not confirmed by 
the senate 
martoches appointment was expected to alleviate that problem 
because he has already been through the confirmation process in his 
current treasury post 
