stability and leadership to the agency during the transition he 
also said he would appoint fiechter as his principal deputy 
director 
martoche takes over the reins of the agency overseeing the 
restructuring of the troubled sampl industry and will preside over a 
growing list of lawsuits against savings industry executives 
accused of illegal lending practices 
wall criticized in congress for underestimating the sampl crisis 
and acting slowly against the californiabased lincoln savings and 
loan association announced dec 4 he would resign as soon as the 
administration found a replacement 
however as the months passed wall indicated he was anxious to 
leave soon 
martoche is currently assistant secretary of the treasury for 
enforcement overseeing the secret service the customs service and 
the agencys drugintervention programs 
the office of thrift supervision formerly known as the federal 
home loan bank board was extensively overhauled last year as part 
of the 10year 150 billion sampl rescue legislation 
the measure placed the agency under the control of the treasury 
department and removed many of its previous powers under the 
legislation a new agency the resolution trust corp is charged 
with selling or closing hundreds of insolving sampl associations 
