a storm moving out of the rockies and onto the plains blasted 
wyoming and colorado with heavy wet snow tuesday closing schools 
and hundreds of miles of highway and shutting down the wyoming 
legislature 
wyomings laramie range near granite mountain had picked up 3 to 
