the supreme court on tuesday granted 
bail to sen juan ponce enrile the opposition leader who was 
arrested in connection with decembers bloody coup attempt but it 
delayed ruling on the validity of a charge against him 
the decision appeared to be a setback for president corazon 
aquinos government which accused enrile last week of rebellion 
with murder 
