windshield wipers in the 1960s only to discover automakers werent 
interested he went to court in the 1980s after the wipers became 
standard equipment and recently won a judgment against ford motor 
co 
graff bought the patent rights to bedfellows last year and so 
far has sold little more than 250 sets for under 30 his chief 
competition is the standard hollywood bedframe that sells for about 
the same price there the similarities end 
the bedframe doesnt look remotely like one it more resembles 
sets of bicycle handlebars put together and fastened to the 
underside of a box spring mattress its advantages over a 
conventional frame says graff are considerable 
bedfellows for a fullsize boxspring weighs about six pounds 
onefourth the weight of a standard frame that cuts into the 
considerable costs of shipping and eases the chores of storage and 
store display says graff 
customers get a break too the assembled frame is easier to 
move even with mattress and box springs because the weight is 
distributed on eight points instead of four 
its odd configuration eliminates exposed rails and legs ending 
the ageold menace of stubbed toes and barked shins ive bumped 
my toe enough times in the middle of the night to realize there 
some merit there graff says 
